   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>App Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Develop</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Custom Settings</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> and click <uicontrol>Manage</uicontrol> for Config Custom
               Classes.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> for Custom Classes.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the Deal Maximizer Callback Class enter
                     <i>
                  <userinput>Apttus_CPQOpti.DealMaximizerCallback</userinput>
               </i>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <result id="result_df5_d33_rcc">Deal guidance information can now be displayed in the shopping
         cart when it is available.</result>
      <div>
         <p>You can now configure color bands, dimensions, dimension sets, and deal guidance rules.</p>
      </div>
